sun.jvm.hotspot.oops

Class DefaultOopVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.jvm.hotspot.oops.DefaultOopVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FieldVisitor, OopVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ObjectReader.FieldSetter

    public class DefaultOopVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements OopVisitor
    A DefaultOopVisitor implements basic no-op OopVisitor functionality except that the setObj() and getObj() methods are implemented properly.
